%h1
  Congrats!
  - if @milestone.tagline.present?
    You earned the #{@milestone.tagline} badge!
  - else
    You passed #{friendly_display_of_threshold(@milestone, @user)} without using a car.

- if @milestone.badge.attached?
  = image_tag @milestone.badge

%p
  Head to
  = link_to "your #CarFreeChallenge dashboard", url_for(controller: "home", action: "dashboard")
  to share your achievement.

%small
  Don't want to receive these emails?
  = link_to "Unsubscribe", url_for(controller: "users", action: "unsubscribe", id: @user.id)